- THE ARTIST
HAS OBVIOUSLY BEEN INFLUENCED

32:15.101 --> 32:17.603
BY THE WORK
OF THE ABSTRACT EXPRESSIONISTS--

32:17.636 --> 32:20.639
DE KOONING.
GOTTLIEB.

32:20.672 --> 32:22.274
KLEIN.
- LINDSAY!

32:22.308 --> 32:24.977
LONG TIME, BABE.

32:25.011 --> 32:27.513
- TOO LONG.
MWAH.

32:27.546 --> 32:29.181
MWAH.

32:29.215 --> 32:30.482
CONGRATULATIONS ON THE SHOW.
- THANKS.

32:30.516 --> 32:32.451
- HOW'S IT GOING?
- SOLD THREE ALREADY.

32:32.484 --> 32:33.585
- NOT BAD.

32:33.619 --> 32:35.587
- A COUPLE MORE,
I'M ON MY WAY TO RIO.

32:35.621 --> 32:37.189
- [chuckling]

32:37.223 --> 32:38.590
