32:38.624 --> 32:40.292
THIS IS JUSTIN TAYLOR.

32:40.326 --> 32:41.427
THIS IS ADRIENNE BENNETT.

32:41.460 --> 32:42.628
SHE'S THE ARTIST.

32:42.661 --> 32:44.730
JUSTIN'S AN ARTIST TOO.

32:44.763 --> 32:46.465
HE WAS JUST COMMENTING
ON THIS PIECE,

32:46.498 --> 32:49.268
HOW MUCH HE LIKED
THE SPONTANEITY, THE ANGER.

32:49.301 --> 32:52.438
- I WAS IN A MOOD THAT DAY.

32:52.471 --> 32:55.207
SO WHAT KIND OF STUFF YOU DO?

32:55.241 --> 32:58.044
- I DON'T ANYMORE.
I GAVE IT UP.

32:58.077 --> 32:59.378
- HMM.

32:59.411 --> 33:00.779
CHRIST,
IF I COULDN'T WORK,

33:00.812 --> 33:02.348
I'D WHEEL MYSELF OFF A CLIFF.

33:02.381 --> 33:06.385
- HOW DO YOU? I MEAN--
- WORK?

33:06.418 --> 33:08.387
UH, THE WAY TWO SNAILS FUCK:

33:08.420 --> 33:11.457
VERY SLOWLY.

33:11.490 --> 33:13.425
[laughter]

33:13.459 --> 33:15.227
I GOT THIS CONTRAPTION I CALL
THE ONE-ARM BANDIT

33:15.261 --> 33:16.728
THEY STRAPPED TO MY GOOD ARM.

33:16.762 --> 33:18.564
THAT'S THE WAY
I DIRECT THE BRUSH.

33:18.597 --> 33:20.299
- SOUNDS HARD.

33:20.332 --> 33:22.101
- SO WHAT'S EASY
BESIDES COMPLAINING?

33:22.134 --> 33:23.535
- AS IF YOU NEVER DID THAT.

33:23.569 --> 33:27.339
- OH, BACK OFF, BITCH.
I'LL ROLL OVER YOUR FOOT.

33:27.373 --> 33:29.741
NOW I'LL ADMIT
I WASN'T TOO PLEASED

33:29.775 --> 33:32.544
AFTER DOING A SPIN-OUT
ON THE PENN-LINCOLN PARKWAY

33:32.578 --> 33:35.081
TO WAKE UP AND DISCOVER
MY TAP-DANCING DAYS WERE OVER.

33:35.114 --> 33:37.049
LET ALONE PAINTING.

33:37.083 --> 33:38.750
IN FACT,
I WAS OFFERING BIG BUCKS

33:38.784 --> 33:42.054
TO ANYONE WHO'D SHOOT ME.

33:42.088 --> 33:45.057
YOU MUST BE FEELING
THE SAME WAY.

33:48.160 --> 33:52.198
IT AIN'T THE END
OF THE WORLD, KID.

33:52.231 --> 33:56.102
UNLESS YOU WANT IT TO BE.

33:56.135 --> 33:59.205
NOW PICK A PAINTING.

33:59.238 --> 34:01.273
- HMM?
- I WANT YOU TO HAVE ONE.

34:01.307 --> 34:03.709
- ADRIENNE.
- DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

34:03.742 --> 34:05.711
THERE'S PLENTY MORE
WHERE THESE CAME FROM.

34:10.716 --> 34:13.152
- I JUST CALLED THE BIG Q.

34:13.185 --> 34:15.387
THEY SAID THAT YOU
NO LONGER WORK THERE,

34:15.421 --> 34:16.555
THAT YOU QUIT?

34:16.588 --> 34:18.324
- THAT'S RIGHT, MA.

34:18.357 --> 34:20.626
- WHY WOULD YOU DO
A STUPID THING LIKE THAT?

34:20.659 --> 34:23.329
- WELL,
I'M FOLLOWING MY DREAM.

34:23.362 --> 34:25.464
- TO BE UNEMPLOYED?
[door opens]

34:25.497 --> 34:27.133
- LEAVE HIM ALONE, DEB.

34:27.166 --> 34:29.135
- I SHOULD'VE KNOWN
THAT YOU'D BE INVOLVED.

34:29.168 --> 34:30.502
- I HAD NOTHING TO DO WITH IT.

34:30.536 --> 34:32.471
- YEAH, I'VE BEEN HEARING THAT
SINCE YOU WERE 14.

34:32.504 --> 34:33.839
- IT'S HIS LIFE.
- YEAH, THAT'S EASY

34:33.872 --> 34:35.607
FOR YOU TO SAY.
YOU CAN PAY YOUR BILLS.

34:35.641 --> 34:37.476
- WOULD YOU TWO KNOCK IT OFF?

34:37.509 --> 34:39.245
I'M TRYING TO CONCENTRATE.

34:39.278 --> 34:40.279
- ON WHAT?

34:40.312 --> 34:42.281
I'M AUCTIONING SOMETHING
ON EBAY.

34:42.314 --> 34:44.116
- YOUR MOTHER?

34:44.150 --> 34:46.318
DON'T START THE BIDDING
TOO HIGH.

34:46.352 --> 34:48.354
- MY CAPTAIN ASTRO.
VOLUME ONE. ISSUE ONE.

34:48.387 --> 34:50.256
- THE ONE I BOUGHT YOU
FOR YOUR BIRTHDAY?

34:50.289 --> 34:52.891
THAT COST A FUCKING MINT.
- I KNOW.

34:52.924 --> 34:58.197
IF I GET ENOUGH FOR IT,
I'M GOING TO BUY BUZZY'S STORE.

34:58.230 --> 34:59.598
- YOU'RE BUYING
A COMIC BOOK STORE?

34:59.631 --> 35:00.732
THAT'S CRAZY.

35:00.766 --> 35:02.868
- SO IS STAYING IN A JOB
WHERE I'M GOING TO BE MISERABLE

35:02.901 --> 35:05.671
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE.

35:08.407 --> 35:10.476
[thud]
- WHAT'S THE BID AT?

35:10.509 --> 35:13.379
- IT'S STUCK AT $1,000.
- $1,000?

35:13.412 --> 35:15.514
FUCK, IT'S WORTH MORE THAN THAT.
SCOOT OVER.

35:15.547 --> 35:17.183
- IF YOU SAID
YOU WERE REALLY SORRY,

35:17.216 --> 35:18.884
MAYBE THEY'D GIVE YOU
YOUR JOB BACK.

35:18.917 --> 35:20.219
- THERE'S
ONLY A FEW MINUTES LEFT.

35:20.252 --> 35:21.920
- HOW DOES $5,000 SOUND?

35:21.953 --> 35:23.489
- YOU'RE BIDDING ON IT YOURSELF?

35:23.522 --> 35:25.491
- WHY IN THE FUCK
WOULD YOU DO THAT?

35:25.524 --> 35:26.892
YOU ALREADY BOUGHT IT ONCE.

35:26.925 --> 35:28.860
- THE SECRET TO GETTING SOMEONE
TO WANT SOMETHING

35:28.894 --> 35:31.563
IS CONVINCING THEM SOMEONE ELSE
WANTS IT MORE.

35:31.597 --> 35:36.302
- THAT'LL NEVER WORK.
PEOPLE AREN'T THAT STUPID.

35:36.335 --> 35:39.605
- $6,000.

35:39.638 --> 35:42.174
- THEN AGAIN...

35:42.208 --> 35:43.475
[objects rustling]

35:43.509 --> 35:46.412
- HANDY.

35:46.445 --> 35:51.483
SEX MEN.

35:51.517 --> 35:55.687
APES.

35:55.721 --> 35:58.224
SO...

35:58.257 --> 36:01.793
I WILL BRING
THE REST BACK TOMORROW.

36:01.827 --> 36:03.662
- THE REST?

36:03.695 --> 36:05.731
- JUST PUT THEM ON MY CHARGE,
QUENTIN.

36:05.764 --> 36:08.267
- WHICH OF THESE
DO YOU RECOMMEND?

36:08.300 --> 36:10.302
- YOU THINK I WATCH THIS SHIT?

36:10.336 --> 36:12.371
ASK HIM.
HE'S SEEN THEM ALL.

36:12.404 --> 36:14.740
- LET ME SEE.

36:14.773 --> 36:16.608
YOUR ASS-LICKED PARK.

36:16.642 --> 36:17.876
IT'S AN EXCELLENT RIMMING SCENE

36:17.909 --> 36:20.746
BETWEEN A PALEONTOLOGIST
AND A STEGOSAURUS.

36:20.779 --> 36:23.415
FORREST DUMP.
SOME IDIOT GIVES NIXON

36:23.449 --> 36:24.950
A PLATE JOB IN THE OVAL OFFICE.

36:24.983 --> 36:26.985
OH, DEFINITELY THIS ONE.

36:27.018 --> 36:29.421
ARM 'N HEAD IN.
IT'S GOT THE BEST FISTING SCENE

36:29.455 --> 36:31.290
ON AN ASTEROID HEADED
TO EARTH EVER FILMED.

36:31.323 --> 36:36.428
- WOW.
YOU'RE AMAZING.

36:36.462 --> 36:38.330
- NO, YOU ARE AMAZING.

36:38.364 --> 36:40.432
ALTHOUGH I WOULDN'T CALL KNOWING
EVERY BOY-BANG FLICK

36:40.466 --> 36:42.368
EVER MADE
A SIGNIFICANT CONTRIBUTION

36:42.401 --> 36:43.402
TO CULTURAL LITERACY.

36:43.435 --> 36:44.536
- HEY, MISSY BIG-WORDS.

36:44.570 --> 36:46.305
I'M NOT ASHAMED OF LOVING PORN.

36:46.338 --> 36:48.307
PORNOGRAPHY HAPPENS
TO SERVE AN IMPORTANT

36:48.340 --> 36:49.741
AND PROFOUNDLY HUMANE SERVICE.

36:49.775 --> 36:51.310
- OH, THIS OUGHT TO BE GOOD.

36:51.343 --> 36:54.012
- ALL RIGHT, TAKE A GUY LIKE ME
RENTING A VIDEO, OKAY?

36:54.045 --> 36:55.981
WHAT ARE MY CHOICES?

36:56.014 --> 36:57.449
A MORONIC COMEDY,

36:57.483 --> 37:00.586
A COP DRAMA
STARRING SOME BRAINLESS ACTOR

37:00.619 --> 37:03.555
SHOOTING OFF HIS "WIDDLE" GUN,
OR...

37:03.589 --> 37:07.259
AN EXOTIC FANTASY LAND
FILLED WITH BEAUTIFUL MEN,

37:07.293 --> 37:09.828
ALL OF WHOM ARE THERE FOR
THE SOLE PURPOSE OF PLEASING ME?

37:09.861 --> 37:11.563
- AHH.
- SEE, IT'S MY CHANCE

37:11.597 --> 37:12.864
TO BE BRIAN KINNEY.

37:12.898 --> 37:14.400
FUCK ANYONE I WANT.
- ALL RIGHT. ALL RIGHT.

37:14.433 --> 37:15.667
ALL RIGHT.
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.

37:15.701 --> 37:17.035
SO YOU GET YOUR ROCKS OFF
TO SOME DREAM BOY,

37:17.068 --> 37:20.706
BUT YOU GOTTA ADMIT,
IT'S A DIRTY BUSINESS.

37:20.739 --> 37:23.509
- WHAT, MAKING PEOPLE HAPPY?

37:23.542 --> 37:25.777
IT'S A LOT MORE THAN I CAN SAY
FOR MY JOB.

37:25.811 --> 37:29.381
ALL I DO IS CRUNCH NUMBERS SO
SOME ASSHOLE CAN CHEAT UNCLE SAM

37:29.415 --> 37:30.749
OUT OF A FEW EXTRA BUCKS.

37:30.782 --> 37:32.351
SEE, NOW THAT'S
WHAT I CALL PORN.

37:32.384 --> 37:33.819
THERE'S NO REDEEMING
SOCIAL VALUE WHATSOEVER.

37:33.852 --> 37:36.755
- I THINK YOU PROVIDE AN
EXTREMELY IMPORTANT SERVICE.

37:36.788 --> 37:38.457
- PREPARING YOUR TAXES?

37:38.490 --> 37:40.526
YEAH, GREAT, WHEN'S THE LAST
TIME IT MADE YOU COME?

37:40.559 --> 37:43.762
- 1998.
I GOT A BIG REFUND.

37:43.795 --> 37:45.831
I GOTTA GET TO COURT.

38:10.856 --> 38:13.925
- YEAH.
GO FOR IT.

